Ok, I applied Andrew Morton's updated CDROMREADAUDIO DMA patch from Jan 2003 
(
http://lwn.net/Articles/19386/
) to kernel 2.4.25, and everything seems to 
work fine now.
Thanks, Jens & Lee!
